name: CalendarSync
short: Sync Discord events to Google Calendar
description: Automatically syncs Discord scheduled events to a Google Calendar, making event management easier for your community.
end_user_data_statement: This cog stores Google Calendar credentials for the server. No personal user data is stored.
install_msg: Thanks for installing CalendarSync! First, set up your Google Calendar credentials using `[p]calendarset credentials` and calendar ID using `[p]calendarset setcalendar`.
author: Drago Prime
